### ============================================
### PRODUCTS - GET PRODUCTS
### ============================================

### 1. Get Products - Default --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

###

### 2. Get Products - With Pagination --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?limit=10&offset=0

###

### 3. Get Products - Filter By Category --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=Men

###

### 4. Get Products - Filter By Minimum Price --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?min_price=500000

###

### 5. Get Products - Multiple Filters --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?limit=5&offset=0&category=Men&min_price=500000

###

### ============================================
### PRODUCTS - GET PRODUCT DETAIL
### ============================================

### 6. Get Product Detail - Success --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

###

### 7. Get Product Detail - Product Not Found --- ok 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{invalidProductId}}

###

### ============================================
### PRODUCTS - SEARCH
### ============================================

### 8. Search Products - Success --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=dior

###

### 9. Search Products - Another Keyword --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=chanel

###

### 10. Search Products - No Result --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=thisproductdoesnotexist

###

### 11. Search Products - Empty Keyword --- ok 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=

###

### 12. Search Products - Pagination --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=dior&limit=5&offset=0

###

### ============================================
### CATEGORIES
### ============================================

### 13. Get Categories - Success --- ok 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

###


### ============================================
### PRODUCTS - CREATE PRODUCT
### ============================================

### 14. Create Product - Success --- ok 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Office Perfume",
  "brand": "Office Brand",
  "categoryId": "b5123a45-7a0d-443b-be92-d6bd1e34ccc1",
  "description": "Warm spicy fragrance.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/noir-extreme.jpg"
}

###

### 15. Create Product - Missing Token --- ok 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tom Ford Noir Extreme",
  "brand": "Tom Ford",
  "category": "Men",
  "description": "Warm spicy fragrance.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/noir-extreme.jpg"
}

###

