Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 28. Delete Product - Missing Token --- ok 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

###

### 29. Delete Product - Invalid Token --- ok 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

###

### 30. Delete Product - Non Admin User --- ok 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clientAccessToken}}

###

### 31. Delete Product - Product Not Found --- ok 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{invalidProductId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

